id: pm-2awd
title: Single-source extension manifest and policy examples in docs
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: docs/EXTENSIONS.md embeds extension manifest and policy examples that duplicate runnable example files. Manifest v2 provenance/sandbox/permissions/capabilities examples appear in docs/EXTENSIONS.md:145-170 and docs/examples/policy-restricted-extension/manifest.json:1-21 plus docs/examples/starter-extension/manifest.json:1-32; policy config examples appear in docs/EXTENSIONS.md:193-217 and docs/examples/policy-restricted-extension/README.md:26-59. Existing pm-w98k covers source-code extension contract constants and pm-axd1 covers production/test default objects, not docs/example snippet drift."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[4]: dedup,docs,examples,extensions
